627
00:27:42,820 --> 00:27:43,850
Besides Boxing...

628
00:27:45,100 --> 00:27:46,100
How about this?

629
00:27:46,660 --> 00:27:47,580
Come do real estate with me.

630
00:27:48,100 --> 00:27:49,020
