00:31:09,580 --> 00:31:10,520
Ms. Liu Yan!

695
00:31:11,080 --> 00:31:11,940
Hello.

696
00:31:11,940 --> 00:31:13,240
Sorry, about your agreement,

697
00:31:13,240 --> 00:31:14,730
there's an urgent issue now.

