741
00:32:46,980 --> 00:32:48,340
So please understand.

742
00:32:48,340 --> 00:32:49,210
Lu Tianchi,

743
00:32:49,320 --> 00:32:50,830
if you can't make sense of it,

744
00:32:50,830 --> 00:32:52,020
