747
00:32:54,370 --> 00:32:55,460
Please have a look.

748
00:32:55,980 --> 00:32:56,950
What does it add?

749
00:32:57,620 --> 00:32:58,920
Previously, our agreement

750
00:32:58,920 --> 00:33:00,200
required both parties to be

751
00:33:00,210 --> 00:33:01,500
(Call me and you'll win. There must be money.)
