757
00:33:08,860 --> 00:33:09,900
Just focus on your search.

758
00:33:09,900 --> 00:33:11,140
If you find her, I'll come back.

759
00:33:11,140 --> 00:33:12,010
Finding Jiang Fang

760
00:33:12,010 --> 00:33:13,300
is my responsibility to you.

761
00:33:13,300 --> 00:33:14,570
But I don't have the right

762
00:33:14,570 --> 00:33:15,420
to confine Jiang Fang.

763
00:33:16,070 --> 00:33:18,170
So, in this clause,

764
00:33:18,170 --> 00:33:19,010
