from Beijing by rocket.

771
00:33:28,050 --> 00:33:28,940
Miss Liu,

772
00:33:28,980 --> 00:33:30,600
that's why I had to put this condition

773
00:33:30,600 --> 00:33:32,010
into our supplementary agreement.

774
00:33:32,340 --> 00:33:33,730
Because you're not in Jaya,

775
00:33:33,730 --> 00:33:35,180
you miss seeing Jiang Fang.

776
00:33:35,180 --> 00:33:36,380
That doesn't count as my breach

777
00:33:36,380 --> 00:33:37,680
and agreement completed, right?

778
00:33:37,820 --> 00:33:39,590
So if we hit the next stage,

779
00:33:39,590 --> 00:33:41,380
which makes finding Jiang Fang harder,

780
00:33:41,380 --> 00:33:42,480
all losses can't be counted

781
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:44,140
within my responsibility.

782
00:33:44,350 --> 00:33:45,350
I need to put all of this

783
00:33:45,350 --> 00:33:46,580
down in writing, officially.

784
00:33:46,700 --> 00:33:47,860
