I can't return to Beijing, right?

805
00:34:22,540 --> 00:34:23,500
Miss Liu,

806
00:34:23,660 --> 00:34:24,580
I think

807
00:34:25,140 --> 00:34:26,770
you can't summarize it

808
00:34:26,770 --> 00:34:27,620
