00:37:45,720 --> 00:37:46,570
In winter,

864
00:37:47,880 --> 00:37:49,290
I was always freezing.

865
00:37:49,770 --> 00:37:51,080
Your sis would give me

866
00:37:52,330 --> 00:37:54,090
her thick leggings.

867
00:37:54,090 --> 00:37:55,160
She didn't wear them.

868
00:37:57,550 --> 00:38:00,020
That's because I just hate them.

869
00:38:06,760 --> 00:38:07,890
Your sis

870
00:38:08,190 --> 00:38:10,380
is not good at expressing herself.

871
00:38:12,270 --> 00:38:13,340
Drink less.

872
00:38:13,540 --> 00:38:14,400
It's fine.

873
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:15,960
We're...

874
00:38:16,820 --> 00:38:20,440
developing on our own paths.

875
00:38:21,550 --> 00:38:22,480
But

876
00:38:22,860 --> 00:38:25,100
we're destined

877
00:38:26,660 --> 00:38:28,420
to stay together forever.

878
00:38:31,540 --> 00:38:33,100
Even though this time,

879
00:38:33,450 --> 00:38:34,620
she won't come back with me.

880
00:38:35,880 --> 00:38:37,770
But your sis will eventually

881
00:38:37,770 --> 00:38:39,060
return to Beijing.

882
00:38:39,230 --> 00:38:41,020
Do you get that?

883
00:39:27,200 --> 00:39:28,130
Are you angry with me?

884
00:39:32,300 --> 00:39:33,370
If you don't say, I'll go.

885
00:39:35,650 --> 00:39:37,580
All we talked about last night

886
00:39:38,830 --> 00:39:39,670
was for nothing, huh?

887
00:39:41,640 --> 00:39:42,860
I need to find Jiang Fang.

888
00:39:44,230 --> 00:39:45,270
I have to see her face

889
00:39:45,270 --> 00:39:46,240
at first sight.

890
00:39:47,580 --> 00:39:48,620
There are so many questions

891
00:39:48,620 --> 00:39:49,580
I want to ask her.

892
00:39:50,020 --> 00:39:51,350
I can't let her slip away again.

893
00:39:52,970 --> 00:39:54,640
She can't just run off, you know?

894
00:39:55,590 --> 00:39:57,220
About looking for Jiang Fang,

895
00:39:58,360 --> 00:39:59,220
I understand it

896
00:39:59,220 --> 00:40:00,230
and support you.

897
00:40:00,540 --> 00:40:01,380
But ultimately,

898
00:40:01,880 --> 00:40:03,210
you need to think about yourself.

899
00:40:03,560 --> 00:40:04,770
Can't we just...

900
00:40:05,720 --> 00:40:06,830
live our own lives?

901
00:40:10,120 --> 00:40:11,100
Well,

902
00:40:12,290 --> 00:40:13,520
I feel like I have never thought about

903
00:40:13,520 --> 00:40:14,500
what I actually like.

904
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:16,020
It's like when someone asks about

905
00:40:16,200 --> 00:40:17,810
what flavor of ice cream you like,

906
00:40:17,810 --> 00:40:18,880
you say chocolate.

907
00:40:19,500 --> 00:40:20,740
As time goes by,

908
00:40:20,740 --> 00:40:22,740
you and everyone else really believe

909
00:40:22,740 --> 00:40:24,490
that chocolate's your favorite.

910
00:40:26,090 --> 00:40:28,450
But I've never tried other flavors.

911
00:40:31,830 --> 00:40:32,670
I have no choice.

912
00:40:34,270 --> 00:40:35,670
I need you to understand me.

913
00:40:37,250 --> 00:40:38,660
I can't go back to Beijing yet.

914
00:40:38,660 --> 00:40:40,980
Yeah, I'm trying to understand.

915
00:40:41,370 --> 00:40:42,790
I have to find Jiang Fang.

916
00:40:43,370 --> 00:40:45,220
I know no one supports me

917
00:40:45,340 --> 00:40:46,830
when it comes to finding Jiang Fang.

918
00:40:50,030 --> 00:40:52,280
But that's because they don't know her.

919
00:40:52,280 --> 00:40:53,690
You're different, Wang Yang.

920
00:41:00,780 --> 00:41:02,270
I'll remember what you said

921
00:41:02,270 --> 00:41:03,180
last night forever.

922
00:41:05,860 --> 00:41:07,100
Alright, you should go back now.

923
00:41:08,400 --> 00:41:09,720
If you don't go, you'll miss the flight.

924
00:41:15,970 --> 00:41:17,590
It's okay. If anything comes up,

925
00:41:17,590 --> 00:41:18,540
I'll come and find you again.

926
00:41:18,710 --> 00:41:20,390
If the mountain
doesn't come to me, I'll go to it.

927
00:41:22,140 --> 00:41:23,200
Stop it. As long as you're here,

928
00:41:23,210 --> 00:41:24,720
I'll have to look after you.

929
00:41:28,280 --> 00:41:29,980
Beijing is our home.

930
00:41:29,980 --> 00:41:31,160
Just do your best over there.

931
00:41:31,910 --> 00:41:32,970
Otherwise, when I go back,

932
00:41:32,970 --> 00:41:34,130
I won't have any family

933
00:41:34,130 --> 00:41:35,050
to turn to at all.

934
00:41:38,040 --> 00:41:38,940
What are you doing?

935
00:41:42,300 --> 00:41:44,900
(Waiting for you to come back)

936
00:41:45,010 --> 00:41:46,170
Are you bored or what?

937
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:53,510
I'm leaving.

938
00:42:21,380 --> 00:42:26,140
♪Mother, I've grown up♪

939
00:42:28,260 --> 00:42:35,180
♪No longer crave my embrace♪

940
00:42:35,660 --> 00:42:42,380
♪No longer need my approval♪

941
00:42:43,100 --> 00:42:49,540
♪No longer afraid
to realize I'm still here♪

942
00:42:50,500 --> 00:42:53,940
♪Countless disappointments;
nothing left to hope for♪

943
00:42:54,180 --> 00:42:57,860
♪We're falling through the air,
endlessly falling down♪

944
00:42:57,860 --> 00:43:01,380
♪There's nothing we can hold on to♪

945
00:43:01,780 --> 00:43:06,100
♪No ground where we can land safely♪

946
00:43:07,540 --> 00:43:09,420
♪(When all hope is gone)♪

947
00:43:09,420 --> 00:43:15,340
♪Our hearts will break
before the dream ends♪

948
00:43:16,060 --> 00:43:20,020
♪We drift along in this dazzling world♪

949
00:43:20,260 --> 00:43:24,220
♪Stumbling through every change
life brings♪

950
00:43:24,220 --> 00:43:27,260
♪The true courage
is simply not looking back♪

951
